sqce.title: SonarQube CE Log Format
sqce.description: The log format for SonarQube web.log

Persist issues.pattern: ^((?<timestamp>\d{4}.\d{2}.\d{2} \d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2}) (?<level>ERROR|WARN|INFO|DEBUG)( |  )ce\[(?<pid>[\w\-\.\$\+\]]*)\]\[(?<module>[\w\-\.]*)\])(?<action>[\w\ \=\.\-\:\']*)((\|)( cacheSize=(?<cacheSize>[\d\.]+) [\w]+) )(\|)( inserts=(?<inserts>[\d]*) )(\|)( updates=(?<updates>[\d]*) )(\|)( merged=(?<merged>[\d]*) )(\|)( status=(?<status>[\w]*) )(\|)( time=(?<time>[\d]*)ms)

Detect file moves.pattern: ^((?<timestamp>\d{4}.\d{2}.\d{2} \d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2}) (?<level>ERROR|WARN|INFO|DEBUG)( |  )ce\[(?<pid>[\w\-\.\$\+\]]*)\]\[(?<module>[\w\-\.]*)\])(?<action>[\w\ \=\.\-\:\']*)((\|)( reportFiles=(?<reportFiles>[\d]+)) )(\|)( dbFiles=(?<dbFiles>[\d]+)) (\|)( addedFiles=(?<addedFiles>[\d]+)) (\|)(( movedFiles=(?<movedFiles>[\d]*) )(\|)|)( status=(?<status>[\w]*) )(\|)( time=(?<time>[\d]*)ms)

Detect file moves in pull request scope.pattern: ^((?<timestamp>\d{4}.\d{2}.\d{2} \d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2}) (?<level>ERROR|WARN|INFO|DEBUG)( |  )ce\[(?<pid>[\w\-\.\$\+\]]*)\]\[(?<module>[\w\-\.]*)\])(?<action>[\w\ \=\.\-\:\']*)((\|)( reportFiles=(?<reportFiles>[\d]+)) )(\|)( dbFiles=(?<dbFiles>[\d]+)) (\|)( movedFiles=(?<movedFiles>[\d]+)) (\|)( addedFiles=(?<addedFiles>[\d]+)) (\|)( status=(?<status>[\w]*) )(\|)( time=(?<time>[\d]*)ms)

time.description: The ID of the process that generated the message

action.description: The ID of the process that generated the message

status.description: The ID of the process that generated the message

pid.description: The ID of the process that generated the message

module.description: The name of the module that generated the message
